DESCRIPTION:PROFIT FIRST WORKSHOP - ENCORE EVENT with Danielle Mulvey\n\nAgency Solutions LIVE | Thursday\, June 18\, 2026 | 1:00 PM Eastern\n\nMissed our last Agency Solutions call with Mike Michalowicz - HOW TO MAKE YOUR AGENCY PERMANENTLY PROFITABLE - or just want more? Join us for a full one-hour PROFIT FIRST workshop.\n\nDanielle Mulvey delivers a hands-on workshop on how to implement the Profit First concepts. Danielle has built multiple businesses generating over $50 million in annual revenue by rejecting the hope-and-pray approach to cash flow. As host of PROFIT FIRST NATION - the official Profit First podcast - she is Mike's go-to partner for turning his keynotes into actionable workshops.\n\nLet's get ready to IMPLEMENT Profit First.\n\nFree for Agency Network members. Hosted live on Microsoft Teams.\n\nJoin via Microsoft Teams:\nhttps://teams.microsoft.com/meet/263545131017449?p=SElFGWgvxdamtncnn2\n\nMeeting ID: 263 545 131 017 449\nPasscode: Jm6Gz3t7\n\nConnecting Agents - Inspiring Greatness\nAgency Network
